	   <tr><td colspan=2>It depends on the situation and the group.  I usually am attacking and twisting, using my heal song as a taunt if need be.  I twist party ac and magic resist boosts with anthem de arms thrown in most times.  In down time I heal, unless I'm doing the pulling (yes, bards can pull quite nicely if you're careful, thank you very much).  When I get the mana song, I'll use it and the healing song during down time.  If you've got plenty of tanks and healers you can just buff the party and throw in damage songs.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
