	   <tr><td colspan=2>I usually attack and twist as well. I usually twist buffs and debuffs depending on the situation.  Most of the songs work well just by singing them.  Depending on how well organized the group is, i will swap intruments while fighting to add them little added bonuses to your songs.  If you can avoid being the puller, do so.  An aggroed bard can quickly be a dead bard if not played well.  Plus the point of healing the party while someone else does the pulling helps a bit.  Experiment with various combinations of songs and have fun with it<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
