<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=97231139915993></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f97231139915993><tr><td id=headerrow><span id=sj><a href=/strategy/classes.html?class=4&mid=97231139915993>RE: Twisting songs</a></span></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Mon, Oct 23rd 10:29 AM 2000</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Twisting songs is not an ability you gain, it's a strategy that you do yourself.  Since all of your songs will hold their affect for a few rounds after you stop them, you can start one song, stop it, start the next, stop it, start the third, stop it and go back to the first one again.  If done right you can have three songs going all at once.<br><br>Hope that helps.<br><br>Gilderoi<br>Morrell Thule.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
